WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 31]

02:54.620 --> 02:56.530
Why do I always feel like

02:57.500 --> 02:59.010
you're different today?

03:02.430 --> 03:04.150
If she's not Xi,

03:04.390 --> 03:06.020
why did she risk her life to save me?

03:06.050 --> 03:07.550
Give her some time,

03:07.760 --> 03:09.130
and give yourself some time too.

03:10.070 --> 03:11.830
I'll go and decoct the medicine for my master first.

03:30.670 --> 03:31.420
Shuo!

03:31.950 --> 03:33.050
What did you see?

03:33.130 --> 03:34.570
The last Contemplation is in Bodhi Village.

03:34.600 --> 03:35.870
I saw the vision.

03:36.180 --> 03:37.660
I saw myself offering my blood to a cauldron.

03:37.750 --> 03:39.590
As long as we can fulfill the prophetic vision,

03:39.610 --> 03:40.890
we can gather the fifth Contemplation.

03:41.460 --> 03:42.700
Offering blood to a cauldron?

03:43.370 --> 03:44.460
Every prophetic vision

03:44.490 --> 03:45.950
carries hidden danger.

03:45.980 --> 03:47.770
It's not necessarily a good thing to fulfill the vision.

03:50.160 --> 03:52.230
We've already gone through Ning'an City,

03:52.250 --> 03:54.760
Outlanders' City, the Fox Clan, and the Stone Clan.

03:54.790 --> 03:56.600
In fact, every prophetic vision,

03:56.620 --> 03:58.450
whether we intend it or not,

03:58.470 --> 04:00.060
whether we push it or prevent it,

04:00.090 --> 04:01.620
will eventually be fulfilled.

04:01.640 --> 04:03.510
It's as if

04:03.530 --> 04:05.760
there's an unseen hand pushing everything forward.

04:05.790 --> 04:07.380
I think this time will be no different.

04:08.510 --> 04:09.410
Fan Yue,

04:09.800 --> 04:11.470
we can never know what will happen

04:11.490 --> 04:14.220
after the prophetic vision is fulfilled.

04:14.790 --> 04:16.790
But we can never give up.

04:22.770 --> 04:24.760
After we separated at the Old Turtle's place,

04:25.770 --> 04:27.470
did something happen?

04:37.680 --> 04:40.020
Have you already fulfilled the vision in the Contemplation Stone?

04:41.190 --> 04:42.820
But if it's already been fulfilled,

04:43.380 --> 04:45.350
why didn't you mention it to me?

04:50.150 --> 04:51.480
What are you looking at?

04:53.240 --> 04:53.890
Nothing.

04:55.850 --> 04:57.260
How did you hurt your hand?

04:57.740 --> 05:00.150
I accidentally cut it while decocting medicine for my master.

05:00.850 --> 05:01.760
Accidentally?

05:03.330 --> 05:04.170
What's wrong?

05:05.690 --> 05:06.760
Nothing.

05:07.320 --> 05:08.170
Go to sleep.

05:28.780 --> 05:30.550
Her actions are unusual,

05:31.040 --> 05:32.560
but there's no abnormality in her spiritual aura.

05:34.220 --> 05:35.310
Shuo,

05:36.220 --> 05:37.540
what's really going on with you?

05:39.870 --> 05:41.140
Fan Yue,

05:41.280 --> 05:43.670
you underestimated the power of time.

05:44.310 --> 05:45.800
I've existed for 60,000 years.

05:45.820 --> 05:47.020
How could you possibly uncover

05:47.440 --> 05:49.780
what I want to hide so easily?

05:50.720 --> 05:52.530
From now on, I will be Bai Shuo.

05:53.110 --> 05:54.630
And the only one who can stay by your side

05:54.770 --> 05:56.310
is me.

06:04.990 --> 06:07.020
Keep your position in mind.

06:07.050 --> 06:08.250
Don't forget,

06:08.270 --> 06:10.500
everything you have today was given by me,

06:10.550 --> 06:12.560
and I can take it back at any time.

06:18.160 --> 06:20.810
The view of Heart-guarding Cliff is quite nice.

06:21.250 --> 06:22.570
But I heard that

06:22.590 --> 06:23.640
Heart-guarding Cliff

06:23.670 --> 06:26.030
is a place for repentance in Lanling.

06:26.050 --> 06:26.960
What?

06:27.460 --> 06:29.650
The esteemed Sect Leader of Lanling

06:29.680 --> 06:31.360
needs to repent too?

06:32.100 --> 06:33.190
Zhen Yu,

06:33.220 --> 06:35.070
you must be quite audacious

06:35.100 --> 06:37.130
to trespass into Lanling's territory.

06:37.150 --> 06:38.110
What about you?

06:38.140 --> 06:40.990
You stepped over the corpses of your own clan

06:41.010 --> 06:42.590
to rise to where you are today.

06:42.610 --> 06:45.170
You are quite audacious too.

06:45.200 --> 06:47.300
Nonsense.

06:47.840 --> 06:49.350
Calm down.

06:49.940 --> 06:51.380
Once you and I start fighting

06:51.409 --> 06:52.920
and make too much noise,

06:52.950 --> 06:54.250
aren't you afraid that

06:54.360 --> 06:55.850
the secret of Bodhi Village

06:55.880 --> 06:57.630
will be made public?

07:00.010 --> 07:02.570
You're astonished, aren't you?

07:02.670 --> 07:03.420
Fine.

07:03.690 --> 07:05.890
Let me make it clear.

07:07.120 --> 07:08.090
A few days ago,

07:08.120 --> 07:10.350
I happened to visit a place

07:10.370 --> 07:11.960
called Bodhi Village

07:12.240 --> 07:15.280
and found the barrier outside the village quite peculiar.

07:15.340 --> 07:16.310
Among

07:16.330 --> 07:17.640
all the Eternals,

07:17.660 --> 07:19.740
only you have the ability

07:20.710 --> 07:21.910
to set up that barrier.

07:23.460 --> 07:26.120
I don't know what you are talking about.

07:26.150 --> 07:28.980
Today, you trespassed into Lanling and slandered the leader of the Eternals.

07:29.000 --> 07:30.800
As long as I give the signal,

07:30.830 --> 07:32.390
all the Eternals will come,

07:32.409 --> 07:33.380
and Zhen Yu,

07:33.409 --> 07:35.710
you won't stand a chance of surviving.

07:35.740 --> 07:37.710
If you really wanted to make a move,

07:37.730 --> 07:39.409
you would have given the signal long ago.

07:39.470 --> 07:41.280
It's obvious that, rather than killing me,

07:41.580 --> 07:42.900
you're more afraid

07:42.920 --> 07:43.980
of your secret

07:44.000 --> 07:45.760
being discovered by other Eternals.

07:46.690 --> 07:47.740
That day,

07:47.760 --> 07:49.690
after I left Bodhi Village,

07:49.720 --> 07:51.190
driven by curiosity,

07:51.210 --> 07:53.010
I sent someone to investigate.

07:53.450 --> 07:55.180
It led me to discover something

07:55.270 --> 07:56.880
quite interesting.

07:57.420 --> 07:58.740
Would you like to know what it is?

08:01.580 --> 08:03.000
For nearly a century,

08:03.180 --> 08:04.450
or rather,

08:04.490 --> 08:07.370
since you became the Sect Leader of Lanling,

08:07.390 --> 08:09.040
every so often,

08:09.070 --> 08:10.590
someone from the Eternal Race disappears

08:10.610 --> 08:13.600
while carrying out a demon-slaying mission,

08:13.620 --> 08:14.820
and then

08:14.850 --> 08:16.080
their soul lantern extinguishes,

08:16.100 --> 08:17.460
signifying their death.

08:17.580 --> 08:19.240
But strangely,

08:19.420 --> 08:20.930
their bodies

08:20.960 --> 08:22.920
are nowhere to be found.

08:22.940 --> 08:24.920
Do you think this is just a coincidence,

08:24.950 --> 08:27.860
or is someone behind it, doing it on purpose?

08:31.090 --> 08:32.850
And how is the secret hidden behind this

08:32.909 --> 08:35.630
related to Bodhi Village?

08:36.150 --> 08:37.220
Do you think

08:37.270 --> 08:39.980
I should kindly remind the Eternals?

08:43.630 --> 08:45.420
But don't worry.

08:45.900 --> 08:46.760
I understand

08:46.900 --> 08:49.310
that everyone in this world has their secrets.

08:50.020 --> 08:51.300
I will keep yours

08:51.320 --> 08:53.560
for you.

08:53.580 --> 08:54.570
Actually,

08:54.640 --> 08:56.140
I'm here today

08:56.230 --> 08:58.200
to discuss

08:58.220 --> 08:59.530
a collaboration with you.

09:00.140 --> 09:01.540
As

09:01.560 --> 09:03.040
the leader of the Eternals,

09:03.070 --> 09:04.950
how could I collaborate with demons?

09:05.190 --> 09:07.000
The leader of the Eternals?

09:07.090 --> 09:08.520
How impressive.

09:09.490 --> 09:10.850
But what's the use?

09:10.880 --> 09:12.950
Do you have strong influence?

09:13.100 --> 09:14.930
Stop deceiving yourself.

09:15.950 --> 09:17.550
Among the 72 Sects of the Eternals,

09:17.580 --> 09:19.990
how many people truly respect

09:20.110 --> 09:21.440
and admire you?

09:25.260 --> 09:26.650
Today,

09:26.680 --> 09:28.550
I brought you a gift.

09:28.730 --> 09:30.940
This map records

09:30.960 --> 09:32.960
the location of every major demon clan

09:32.990 --> 09:34.830
and their vital weak points.

09:35.330 --> 09:36.330
I believe

09:36.360 --> 09:37.720
it will help you

09:37.740 --> 09:38.900
make new contributions

09:38.930 --> 09:40.260
and elevate your prestige.

09:40.830 --> 09:41.910
From now on,

09:41.940 --> 09:44.470
no one in the Eternal Race will dare challenge you.

09:44.990 --> 09:47.310
What do you want from me?

09:47.380 --> 09:48.530
It's simple.

09:49.040 --> 09:50.090
You just need

09:51.000 --> 09:52.470
to exterminate the Demon Race

09:52.500 --> 09:54.190
and establish unparalleled achievements;

09:54.210 --> 09:55.470
as for me,

09:55.500 --> 09:56.310
I only need

09:56.330 --> 09:59.160
a small amount of demonic power to heal my wounds.

10:01.910 --> 10:04.140
Heal your wounds?

10:04.730 --> 10:07.030
Isn't that like raising a snake to bite us?

10:07.060 --> 10:08.750
Once we cooperate,

10:08.770 --> 10:10.130
I won't be

10:10.160 --> 10:11.590
a threat to you,

10:11.610 --> 10:13.070
but an ally.

10:13.350 --> 10:15.110
I can also help you

10:15.140 --> 10:17.320
get rid of someone's shackles.

10:22.020 --> 10:23.980
Logically,

10:24.050 --> 10:26.360
the Hidden Power should have perished

10:26.390 --> 10:28.960
along with Hidden Lord Mo Li over 60,000 years ago.

10:29.430 --> 10:31.750
But you still possess the Hidden Power.

10:33.120 --> 10:34.480
Zhen Yu,

10:34.500 --> 10:36.320
who exactly are you?

10:36.620 --> 10:38.500
Who I am doesn't matter.

10:38.530 --> 10:39.750
What matters

10:39.900 --> 10:41.600
is that we can cooperate.

10:42.080 --> 10:44.080
This is

10:44.110 --> 10:45.500
the best choice for you right now.

10:57.900 --> 10:59.500
And there's one more thing

10:59.720 --> 11:01.750
I need you to handle.

11:01.960 --> 11:03.680
That old turtle in Lanling...

11:03.710 --> 11:06.160
I've sent him to Bodhi Village.

11:07.400 --> 11:08.800
You're quite ruthless yourself.

11:08.820 --> 11:09.710
Look,

11:09.730 --> 11:11.700
our goals align so well.

11:12.640 --> 11:14.960
I will never betray

11:14.980 --> 11:16.340
your trust.

12:18.550 --> 12:21.000
[Jin Yao]

12:23.580 --> 12:24.670
Senior?

12:26.570 --> 12:28.340
Why are you here alone?

12:28.540 --> 12:30.710
As a person grows older,

12:31.880 --> 12:34.740
they always want to reminisce about something.

12:34.980 --> 12:38.320
Before I realized it, I walked into this Soul Lantern Room.

12:38.750 --> 12:40.030
to see

12:40.070 --> 12:42.000
some old friends from the past.

12:42.550 --> 12:45.040
But when I came in,

12:45.060 --> 12:48.210
I found that the extinguished soul lanterns

12:48.240 --> 12:50.210
had long been moved out.

12:50.240 --> 12:52.330
Though the soul lanterns have been moved out,

12:52.350 --> 12:53.720
their heroic names

12:53.750 --> 12:55.600
will forever remain in the records of the Eternals

12:54.460 --> 12:56.950
[Loyalty Book]

12:55.620 --> 12:56.860
for future generations to pay tribute to.

12:59.350 --> 13:02.530
They sacrificed their lives,

13:03.770 --> 13:06.680
and in return, they only got a few brief lines

13:06.810 --> 13:08.890
in this book,

13:09.420 --> 13:11.420
for future generations to admire.

13:12.690 --> 13:14.820
How many will actually

13:15.800 --> 13:17.490
flip through these records?

13:17.130 --> 13:17.270
[Loyalty Book]

13:17.730 --> 13:20.460
And how many will truly

13:22.120 --> 13:23.440
remember them?

13:24.880 --> 13:26.160
Yu Feng,

13:26.530 --> 13:29.960
whether we are demons, Eternals, or humans,

13:31.590 --> 13:34.160
don't you think we should leave

13:36.680 --> 13:40.070
something meaningful behind as we walk through this world?

13:40.690 --> 13:43.100
Senior, what's wrong with you today?

13:43.300 --> 13:45.020
Didn't you always say that,

13:45.050 --> 13:46.530
whether as a human or an Eternal,

13:46.560 --> 13:49.080
one should live casually, let go of things,

13:49.100 --> 13:50.790
not force anything, and avoid obsession?

13:59.810 --> 14:01.490
Yu Feng,

14:02.210 --> 14:04.320
gather the Lanling disciples.

14:04.530 --> 14:06.290
From today on,

14:06.730 --> 14:08.280
we will attack the Demon Race

14:08.630 --> 14:10.390
and eradicate the demon threat.

14:30.340 --> 14:31.940
They've been keeping their door closed ever since they returned,

14:31.960 --> 14:32.880
not stepping out at all.

14:32.910 --> 14:34.440
Obviously, they're deliberately avoiding me.

14:34.460 --> 14:35.460
You said last night that

14:35.490 --> 14:37.530
they might have been created with puppetry.

14:37.550 --> 14:39.840
Is there a way to break this puppetry?

14:40.220 --> 14:41.310
I don't know much

14:41.340 --> 14:42.980
about the ancient secret techniques.

14:43.000 --> 14:44.340
And what I said

14:44.370 --> 14:45.990
was only a possibility.

14:47.900 --> 14:49.330
Since we can't leave the village for now,

14:49.350 --> 14:50.680
let's stay

14:50.710 --> 14:51.900
and investigate it thoroughly.

14:58.060 --> 14:58.970
What's wrong?

15:00.160 --> 15:01.360
What's wrong?

15:05.530 --> 15:07.260
Shuo has medicine. I'll take you to her.

15:07.280 --> 15:08.590
Don't go to her.

15:08.620 --> 15:10.670
I don't want her to see me like this.

15:10.700 --> 15:11.320
But I can't

15:11.320 --> 15:13.000
just watch you suffer.

15:13.000 --> 15:13.850
Let's go!

15:13.880 --> 15:15.040
No.

15:15.060 --> 15:16.370
Since

15:16.400 --> 15:17.640
I've already decided

15:17.780 --> 15:19.540
to go separate ways with her,

15:19.560 --> 15:20.920
I shouldn't

15:20.950 --> 15:22.690
keep entangling with her.

15:23.240 --> 15:24.270
Xi?

15:26.160 --> 15:28.040
Xi! Xi!

15:39.680 --> 15:41.680
I didn't know you could cook.

15:43.130 --> 15:44.560
I never cooked for you,

15:44.590 --> 15:46.200
but that doesn't mean I can't cook.

15:46.550 --> 15:48.150
The past is the past.

15:48.490 --> 15:49.360
From now on,

15:49.460 --> 15:51.180
I'll cook for you every day.

15:53.890 --> 15:54.720
Shuo!

15:56.110 --> 15:56.900
Shuo!

15:57.450 --> 15:58.460
Shuo.

15:58.610 --> 16:00.680
Her poison flared up. Do you have any antidote to relieve it?

16:09.450 --> 16:11.210
She doesn't have much time left.

16:11.670 --> 16:12.740
What do you mean

16:12.770 --> 16:14.010
by that?

16:14.030 --> 16:15.840
Her poison has reached her heart and veins.

16:15.870 --> 16:17.910
No antidote can help now.

16:41.490 --> 16:42.580
You're awake?

16:43.210 --> 16:44.900
Why the long face?

16:44.920 --> 16:46.390
It's just a little pain.

16:46.420 --> 16:47.660
It'll pass soon.

16:54.050 --> 16:54.980
I'm sorry.

16:57.680 --> 16:58.960
Why are you apologizing

16:58.960 --> 17:00.210
for no reason?

17:00.240 --> 17:01.000
I'm hungry.

17:01.020 --> 17:02.500
I'll go and see what's there to eat.

17:22.010 --> 17:23.200
I'm sorry.

17:24.750 --> 17:26.490
I thought the poison wasn't fatal.

17:27.920 --> 17:29.200
I thought

17:30.140 --> 17:32.140
if you endured the pain, you'd be fine.

17:31.130 --> 17:34.130
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

17:33.050 --> 17:34.640
I was too stupid

17:34.880 --> 17:37.370
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

17:35.420 --> 17:36.550
that I rashly took you away

17:36.550 --> 17:38.640
from the Cold Spring Palace unprepared.

17:38.090 --> 17:42.020
♫I remember that word of concern♫

17:39.690 --> 17:41.470
I was so foolish that I didn't even realize

17:42.540 --> 17:45.800
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

17:43.290 --> 17:44.950
how little time you had left.

17:46.370 --> 17:49.150
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

17:49.300 --> 17:50.950
You've found out?

17:49.950 --> 17:53.210
♫It dried in the wind♫

17:52.630 --> 17:53.940
Yes.

17:53.800 --> 17:55.600
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

17:54.680 --> 17:56.110
These days,

17:56.070 --> 17:59.730
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

17:56.130 --> 17:57.880
I've been thinking about my master

17:57.880 --> 17:59.110
and my parents.

17:59.180 --> 18:01.180
I thought I was suffering,

18:00.440 --> 18:03.770
♫That year, that year♫

18:01.820 --> 18:03.410
but I didn't know the one

18:04.330 --> 18:06.750
who had truly been suffering was you.

18:04.700 --> 18:07.640
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

18:08.250 --> 18:11.690
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

18:12.690 --> 18:13.970
I'm sorry.

18:12.750 --> 18:15.160
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

18:15.650 --> 18:17.120
I'm sorry.

18:15.940 --> 18:19.200
♫That year, that year♫

18:17.470 --> 18:18.830
I'm sorry.

18:20.030 --> 18:23.050
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

18:23.290 --> 18:24.490
Chong Zhao.

18:23.690 --> 18:26.720
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

18:25.210 --> 18:28.250
I don't want to hear "I'm sorry" from you anymore.

18:27.940 --> 18:30.600
♫Layer after layer♫

18:28.270 --> 18:29.660
This poison is called "Heart Devourer."

18:29.690 --> 18:31.930
Once you take it, you can't stop taking it.

18:31.380 --> 18:34.350
♫Another year passed♫

18:31.950 --> 18:33.150
If you stop taking it,

18:33.180 --> 18:35.400
the poison will flare up and cause death within a month.

18:35.430 --> 18:36.800
I already knew that,

18:36.820 --> 18:38.730
and I foresaw the consequences long ago.

18:38.850 --> 18:40.010
Giving up the antidote

18:40.030 --> 18:41.460
and leaving the Cold Spring Palace

18:41.490 --> 18:42.940
was my own choice.

18:42.970 --> 18:44.070
It's not your fault.

18:44.700 --> 18:45.980
I'm going to find Zhen Yu.

18:46.690 --> 18:50.000
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

18:47.050 --> 18:48.590
I'll get the antidote for you.

18:49.690 --> 18:50.770
Chong Zhao,

18:50.620 --> 18:53.280
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

18:53.560 --> 18:57.800
♫I remember that word of concern♫

18:54.510 --> 18:57.230
I don't want you to be controlled by Zhen Yu again.

18:58.370 --> 18:59.930
I worked for him for ten years,

18:58.500 --> 19:01.480
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

18:59.960 --> 19:01.570
and I know exactly what kind of person he is.

19:01.590 --> 19:03.010
As long as he has the bargaining chip,

19:01.970 --> 19:04.840
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

19:03.040 --> 19:04.760
he will use it to the fullest.

19:05.360 --> 19:06.960
So don't go to him.

19:05.780 --> 19:08.760
♫It dried in the wind♫

19:06.980 --> 19:08.690
Don't give him

19:09.070 --> 19:10.710
any chance to use you.

19:09.390 --> 19:10.940
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

19:11.700 --> 19:15.370
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

19:13.810 --> 19:16.180
Thank you for helping me escape from the Cold Spring Palace.

19:16.480 --> 19:19.120
♫That year, that year♫

19:16.810 --> 19:17.980
During this time,

19:18.010 --> 19:20.210
I feel like I'm finally living like a person again.

19:20.060 --> 19:23.350
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

19:20.540 --> 19:22.700
So now, I'm not afraid at all.

19:22.720 --> 19:23.840
And you shouldn't be afraid either,

19:23.870 --> 19:24.950
okay?

19:24.140 --> 19:27.260
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

19:28.410 --> 19:30.610
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

19:31.650 --> 19:34.760
♫That year, that year♫

19:32.660 --> 19:34.940
We've already missed too much time.

19:35.340 --> 19:38.440
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

19:35.590 --> 19:36.720
So,

19:36.740 --> 19:37.920
let's cherish

19:37.920 --> 19:39.550
the last moments we have together.

19:39.200 --> 19:42.250
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

19:41.270 --> 19:43.830
I hope you can respect my decision.

19:43.480 --> 19:46.050
♫Layer after layer♫

19:47.140 --> 19:50.810
♫Another year passed♫

19:55.300 --> 19:59.420
♫Another year passed♫

19:56.000 --> 19:57.000
Okay.

20:05.390 --> 20:06.670
Okay.

20:06.010 --> 20:09.040
♫That year, that year♫

20:09.710 --> 20:12.870
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

20:13.650 --> 20:16.690
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

20:17.940 --> 20:20.550
♫Layer after layer♫

20:20.360 --> 20:21.530
The food has gone cold.

20:21.570 --> 20:22.600
I'll go heat it up.

20:23.770 --> 20:24.810
No need.

20:28.570 --> 20:29.960
Fu Ling doesn't have much time left.

20:30.100 --> 20:32.030
Why do you act like you don't care at all?

20:32.780 --> 20:34.370
Then what do you think I should do?

20:35.370 --> 20:37.070
Her poison has no cure.

20:37.280 --> 20:38.320
I was telling the truth.

20:38.940 --> 20:40.510
Rather than deceive Chong Zhao,

20:40.560 --> 20:42.290
it's better to let him face the truth.

20:43.290 --> 20:45.200
Aren't you afraid Fu Ling really is Bai Xi?

20:45.540 --> 20:47.290
She didn't admit it herself.

20:47.450 --> 20:49.340
Even if she really is Bai Xi,

20:49.630 --> 20:51.310
she doesn't have much time left.

20:51.360 --> 20:53.080
We will eventually be separated.

20:53.100 --> 20:54.770
No matter how reluctant I am,

20:55.020 --> 20:56.330
what can I do?

21:05.280 --> 21:06.990
Shuo would never say such things.

21:08.170 --> 21:09.500
Who exactly are you?

21:22.710 --> 21:24.690
The spiritual power infused this time

21:24.710 --> 21:27.070
is enough to keep her asleep for a while longer.

21:27.100 --> 21:28.410
Divine Maiden, please don't worry.

21:28.430 --> 21:30.410
She's sleeping well here.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.980
We didn't show any flaws.

21:33.590 --> 21:34.590
Flaws?

21:34.710 --> 21:36.540
I'm never afraid of flaws.

21:37.160 --> 21:38.790
So what if they suspect me?

21:38.880 --> 21:41.050
Now that I've occupied Bai Shuo's body

21:41.080 --> 21:42.520
and am protected by divine power,

21:42.540 --> 21:43.870
what can they do to me?

21:50.540 --> 21:51.980
I can tell

21:52.000 --> 21:53.230
you're angry.

21:53.540 --> 21:54.930
You think that by doing this,

21:54.960 --> 21:56.690
you'll get Fan Yue?

21:56.900 --> 21:58.030
Dream on.

22:00.440 --> 22:02.120
You probably don't know

22:02.140 --> 22:04.480
that last night, I was already in bed with Fan Yue,

22:04.510 --> 22:06.140
lying close together.

22:06.160 --> 22:07.640
I will get

22:07.670 --> 22:09.190
everything you can get

22:09.290 --> 22:10.740
and everything

22:10.760 --> 22:12.160
you can't.

22:12.710 --> 22:15.370
I will take everything that belongs to you.

22:15.880 --> 22:17.900
It sounds like

22:18.070 --> 22:19.240
you didn't take my body

22:19.240 --> 22:21.050
only for Fan Yue.

22:21.080 --> 22:23.260
Why do you have such strong hostility towards me?

22:23.820 --> 22:25.410
Because I hate you.

22:25.440 --> 22:27.750
I've hated you for a very long time.

22:27.770 --> 22:29.080
What do you mean?

22:29.110 --> 22:30.470
We've met before?

22:34.740 --> 22:36.020
Keep an eye on her.

22:36.040 --> 22:36.840
Yes.

22:38.570 --> 22:40.250
You haven't answered my question!

22:43.260 --> 22:44.620
A long time ago?

22:45.100 --> 22:46.120
How long ago?

22:48.120 --> 22:49.630
I've brought it for you.

23:00.160 --> 23:02.160
[Wangyou City] [Ning'an City]

23:02.180 --> 23:04.620
[Wolf Clan]

23:11.580 --> 23:13.930
[Wolf Clan] [White Ape Clan]

23:28.180 --> 23:29.460
It's so late.

23:29.480 --> 23:31.000
Instead of staying with Fu Ling,

23:31.030 --> 23:32.440
why did you ask me out?

23:33.180 --> 23:34.650
I need to go to the Cold Spring Palace.

23:35.240 --> 23:36.480
To find Zhen Yu?

23:36.500 --> 23:38.450
Only he has the antidote for Heart Devourer.

23:38.480 --> 23:39.810
Zhen Yu is one of the Demon Kings.

23:39.830 --> 23:41.390
Though he's not fully healed now,

23:41.420 --> 23:42.770
you still can't defeat him.

23:42.790 --> 23:44.610
Do you know the consequences of going there?

23:44.930 --> 23:46.740
I don't know if I'll be able to come back,

23:46.770 --> 23:48.360
so there's something

23:48.380 --> 23:49.770
I think I should tell you.

23:51.500 --> 23:52.780
Actually,

23:54.250 --> 23:55.570
Fu Ling is Bai Xi.

24:03.020 --> 24:04.780
So you knew it all along.

24:04.800 --> 24:06.230
You've been hiding it from me.

24:06.340 --> 24:08.580
I didn't say it before out of respect for her wishes.

24:08.670 --> 24:10.110
I thought it would be best if the rift between you two sisters

24:10.110 --> 24:11.660
could be resolved by yourselves.

24:11.680 --> 24:13.710
But I might not be able to return this time.

24:13.880 --> 24:15.250
Given her personality,

24:15.270 --> 24:16.070
she will probably

24:16.070 --> 24:17.980
never admit that she is Bai Xi in this lifetime.

24:18.000 --> 24:19.110
I don't want you sisters to end up

24:19.110 --> 24:20.950
not recognizing each other,

24:21.000 --> 24:22.440
and I don't want her

24:22.460 --> 24:24.370
to be alone anymore.

24:24.990 --> 24:26.310
You really

24:26.340 --> 24:28.140
love her so much.

24:30.300 --> 24:32.790
She was in the Cold Spring Palace all by herself for ten years.

24:32.820 --> 24:34.940
During her ten years of suffering,

24:34.960 --> 24:37.830
I was growing up in the Governor's Mansion, worry-free and well-fed.

24:37.860 --> 24:40.260
Every time I think about that, I feel more guilty.

24:41.210 --> 24:43.050
She worked so hard to gain her freedom.

24:43.070 --> 24:44.610
She shouldn't end up like this.

24:48.100 --> 24:50.030
I must go find Zhen Yu and get the antidote.

24:50.060 --> 24:51.260
If I don't come back,

24:51.280 --> 24:52.600
please, you must take good care of her.

24:52.970 --> 24:54.170
The world is vast.

24:54.190 --> 24:56.000
Maybe there are other ways to cure the poison.

24:59.220 --> 25:01.150
If Fu Ling really is Bai Xi,

25:01.610 --> 25:03.220
then I should be the one to go.

25:03.600 --> 25:05.160
I know the Cold Spring Palace better than you.

25:05.180 --> 25:07.080
You two sisters have finally reunited.

25:07.210 --> 25:08.300
You should spend more time with her.

25:08.330 --> 25:09.930
But right now, there is a fog surrounding the village.

25:10.020 --> 25:11.930
That is the barrier set by the Divine Maiden.

25:11.950 --> 25:13.240
You can't get out.

25:13.790 --> 25:15.070
Unless...

25:15.700 --> 25:17.690
unless the Divine Maiden no longer exists,

25:17.710 --> 25:19.380
in which case her barrier

25:19.410 --> 25:20.970
will naturally be lifted.

25:26.130 --> 25:27.690
Senior, you're truly

25:27.720 --> 25:29.090
insightful,

25:29.110 --> 25:31.550
able to foresee everything and win from miles away.

25:31.580 --> 25:33.150
Under your strategic deployment,

25:33.180 --> 25:35.990
those demons had no way to escape.

25:36.020 --> 25:37.720
Even those demon head disciples

25:37.720 --> 25:39.760
who had been wanted by the 72 Sects for many years

25:39.780 --> 25:42.010
were slain by our Lanling Sword Technique.

25:42.720 --> 25:43.630
This time,

25:43.650 --> 25:45.130
Lanling can finally

25:45.160 --> 25:47.040
hold its head high.

25:47.330 --> 25:49.940
Remember to stay humble.

25:49.980 --> 25:51.810
Do not act too conspicuously.

25:51.840 --> 25:53.670
As the leading sect of the Eternals,

25:53.690 --> 25:55.650
Lanling must eradicate the demons

25:55.680 --> 25:57.160
and protect the world.

25:57.180 --> 25:58.220
Yes.

25:58.250 --> 25:59.860
I know. Of course I know.

25:59.880 --> 26:00.750
It just that...

26:01.370 --> 26:03.080
Senior, did you get some secret information

26:03.160 --> 26:04.880
from the Demon Race?

26:05.540 --> 26:07.410
Is it from Chong Zhao?

26:07.440 --> 26:08.770
Let me take a look too.

26:08.790 --> 26:09.830
So nosey.

26:09.860 --> 26:11.170
You're not doing anything yourselves.

26:11.190 --> 26:12.110
Do you want me

26:12.110 --> 26:13.950
to just waste my days like you?

26:14.430 --> 26:15.670
Sect Leader,

26:15.690 --> 26:16.970
you are wise and powerful.

26:17.520 --> 26:18.840
Sect Leader,

26:18.860 --> 26:20.100
you're so decisive.

26:20.760 --> 26:22.410
I'll take my leave now.

26:26.770 --> 26:28.490
So mysterious.

26:28.510 --> 26:29.940
Why so serious?

26:30.020 --> 26:31.150
Seriously.

26:32.560 --> 26:33.670
Yu Feng,

26:33.690 --> 26:36.160
are you trying to look elegant and charming again?

26:39.900 --> 26:41.230
Let me ask you something.

26:41.260 --> 26:42.570
How do you see the fact

26:42.590 --> 26:45.270
that the sect leader has been winning

26:45.390 --> 26:46.550
battle after battle these days?

26:50.640 --> 26:51.570
Don't tell anyone else.

26:51.600 --> 26:53.320
-Okay.
-Closer.

26:53.340 --> 26:54.930
I see it with my own eyes.

26:58.740 --> 27:00.440
Why're you leaving? We haven't finished talking.

27:00.470 --> 27:02.270
My mouth doesn't want to talk about it.

27:03.140 --> 27:04.940
I'm just kidding.

27:04.960 --> 27:05.860
What's wrong?

27:06.100 --> 27:07.420
Is there something you can't figure out?

27:07.450 --> 27:08.500
No.

27:09.030 --> 27:10.750
I just have a feeling.

27:10.770 --> 27:11.570
I feel like,

27:11.590 --> 27:13.700
after so many years of tension between the Eternals and demons,

27:13.730 --> 27:15.140
with both sides always on guard,

27:15.160 --> 27:17.230
don't you think it's been a bit too easy for us

27:17.260 --> 27:18.320
to win...

27:18.340 --> 27:19.990
all these battles recently?

27:20.220 --> 27:21.850
Did you catch a fever and lose your mind?

27:21.960 --> 27:24.640
Why are you talking nonsense if you don't have a fever?

27:24.860 --> 27:26.420
Lanling's victories

27:26.450 --> 27:28.260
have made the demons tremble

27:28.320 --> 27:30.010
and have established our reputation among the Eternals.

27:30.030 --> 27:30.990
Isn't it a good thing?

27:31.020 --> 27:31.780
It is,

27:31.800 --> 27:33.390
-but…
-Then isn't that enough?

27:33.420 --> 27:34.700
Sect Leader

27:34.720 --> 27:35.960
worked diligently,

27:35.990 --> 27:37.720
putting his heart and soul into this,

27:37.740 --> 27:39.070
and earned this glory.

27:39.100 --> 27:39.980
How...

27:40.000 --> 27:41.750
How can you question him?

27:42.200 --> 27:43.490
I'm overthinking it, okay?

27:43.850 --> 27:45.170
Your worries

27:45.940 --> 27:46.900
are heavier than your weight.

27:48.930 --> 27:50.160
I won't talk to you anymore.

27:50.190 --> 27:52.550
I'm going back to my room to get some good sleep.

28:10.950 --> 28:12.230
I can't give up.

28:12.250 --> 28:13.840
Fan Yue is still out there waiting for me.

28:13.870 --> 28:15.110
And there's Xi.

28:15.130 --> 28:16.590
I need to go back and cure her poison.

28:16.590 --> 28:18.210
Stop wasting your energy.

28:18.230 --> 28:20.480
This sea of consciousness is created by my divine power.

28:20.500 --> 28:21.690
You can't break through it.

28:21.720 --> 28:24.190
Your face really is useful.

28:24.220 --> 28:26.410
Now Fan Yue cherishes and cares for me.

28:26.430 --> 28:27.840
All his thoughts

28:27.870 --> 28:29.070
are on me.

28:29.090 --> 28:30.640
Do you think

28:30.670 --> 28:31.660
I'll believe you?

28:32.100 --> 28:33.620
I know Fan Yue.

28:33.650 --> 28:35.020
You can't deceive him.

28:35.050 --> 28:36.610
He will definitely find me.

28:36.690 --> 28:38.360
You don't have a chance now.

28:38.380 --> 28:40.900
I no longer need Luan Zhu's body.

28:40.930 --> 28:42.780
Once my body dies,

28:42.800 --> 28:45.080
your soul will vanish with it.

28:45.110 --> 28:46.220
Bai Shuo,

28:46.240 --> 28:48.870
soon everything you have

28:49.150 --> 28:50.950
will belong to me.

28:50.970 --> 28:53.430
You said you've hated me for a long time.

28:53.790 --> 28:55.350
But before I entered Bodhi Village,

28:55.350 --> 28:56.630
I had never seen you.

28:56.740 --> 28:57.680
Luan Zhu,

28:57.880 --> 28:58.930
is it really me

28:59.140 --> 29:00.200
that you hate?

29:00.200 --> 29:01.670
Of course.

29:01.700 --> 29:02.870
You've forgotten your past,

29:02.890 --> 29:04.190
but I haven't.

29:04.210 --> 29:05.450
I will never forget

29:05.480 --> 29:07.080
what you did.

29:07.190 --> 29:08.470
My past?

29:10.540 --> 29:11.970
Is my past somehow

29:11.990 --> 29:13.150
related to the Divine Race?

29:13.170 --> 29:14.980
So what?

29:15.110 --> 29:16.930
You're about to die.

29:17.300 --> 29:18.270
Bai Shuo,

29:18.960 --> 29:21.390
just watch yourself slowly fade away

29:21.410 --> 29:23.840
in this dark place.

29:24.440 --> 29:25.920
I will become you,

29:25.950 --> 29:27.240
replace you,

29:27.390 --> 29:29.320
and take everything that belongs to you.

29:31.280 --> 29:32.830
Be clear with me.

29:32.850 --> 29:34.070
What past do I have?

29:34.090 --> 29:36.160
What grudge do we have between us?

29:41.880 --> 29:43.220
The Divine Race?

29:43.950 --> 29:46.060
Why am I related to the Divine Race?

29:48.120 --> 29:50.470
Divine Lord, you are the star of this world,

29:50.570 --> 29:51.890
and I, Yuan,

29:51.920 --> 29:53.050
deeply admire you.

29:53.070 --> 29:54.110
I think our Xing Yue Pavilion is too lonely.

29:54.140 --> 29:55.450
From today on,

29:55.470 --> 29:56.800
you'll be my divine attendant.

29:56.830 --> 29:57.610
Divine Lord,

29:57.630 --> 29:59.000
this is the most mysterious and splendid

29:59.030 --> 30:00.900
Lunar Hidden Sea of our Lunar Race.

30:00.920 --> 30:03.480
We've spent 100 years together, sharing the same feelings.

30:03.590 --> 30:05.110
In the past 100 years,

30:06.650 --> 30:08.370
have you ever

30:08.930 --> 30:10.330
truly cared for me?

30:13.230 --> 30:14.080
Don't!

30:18.170 --> 30:20.190
Why do I have these memories?

30:20.570 --> 30:21.880
Who is the person

30:21.900 --> 30:22.900
in my memories?

30:23.610 --> 30:24.910
Who am I?

30:25.460 --> 30:26.180
Luan Zhu.

30:26.670 --> 30:28.430
She must know the whole truth.

30:28.450 --> 30:30.050
I must get out of here.

30:31.860 --> 30:34.990
Chong Zhao has already begun to suspect you two.

30:35.020 --> 30:36.860
-Divine Maiden, please forgive us.
-Divine Maiden, please don't be angry.

30:36.880 --> 30:38.090
Stop it.

30:38.210 --> 30:40.170
Since there are already suspicions,

30:40.190 --> 30:42.270
there's no need to drag it out any longer.

30:42.300 --> 30:44.220
Coincidentally, Jin Yao also has a request.

30:44.240 --> 30:45.280
Tonight,

30:45.310 --> 30:46.830
you two will go and kill Fu Ling.

30:47.480 --> 30:48.490
What about Chong Zhao?

30:48.550 --> 30:50.950
His life is still of use to me.

30:53.530 --> 30:54.570
Divine Maiden,

30:54.590 --> 30:56.070
should we also kill that old turtle

30:56.100 --> 30:57.660
locked in the back mountain?

30:57.680 --> 30:58.870
Why are you in such a hurry?

30:59.160 --> 31:00.530
His skills

31:00.550 --> 31:01.880
will eventually be yours.

31:02.420 --> 31:04.380
Thank you, Divine Maiden.

31:06.310 --> 31:07.870
Watch over my body

31:08.110 --> 31:09.720
and don't let anyone get close to it,

31:10.430 --> 31:11.730
except for Chong Zhao.

31:11.850 --> 31:13.400
Yes, Divine Maiden.

31:27.530 --> 31:29.200
Luan Zhu's spiritual power is profound.

31:29.570 --> 31:31.500
I'm this close to her, yet she shows no reaction.

31:32.160 --> 31:33.590
Has she truly fallen into a deep sleep?

31:52.280 --> 31:53.640
Why don't you do it?

31:55.290 --> 31:56.290
Shuo?

31:56.310 --> 31:56.980
Why are you here?

31:57.010 --> 31:58.390
I was afraid you might be in danger.

31:58.410 --> 32:00.100
The mist barrier was set by her.

32:00.130 --> 32:01.820
Before she can resist,

32:01.890 --> 32:02.740
Chong Zhao,

32:02.770 --> 32:04.010
kill her.

32:08.200 --> 32:09.360
Only by killing her

32:09.380 --> 32:10.750
can you leave the village to find Zhen Yu

32:10.780 --> 32:12.430
and get the antidote to save Xi.

32:12.660 --> 32:14.780
To harm others to achieve one's goals

32:14.810 --> 32:16.290
is not the way of an Eternal.

32:16.310 --> 32:17.230
Without the antidote,

32:17.260 --> 32:18.890
Xi will surely die within ten days.

32:18.910 --> 32:20.430
Don't you care about Xi?

32:20.470 --> 32:21.540
Chong Zhao,

32:21.570 --> 32:22.850
there's only one way,

32:22.870 --> 32:23.950
and you have no choice.

32:24.480 --> 32:25.480
Kill her.

32:28.330 --> 32:30.000
Since you want to kill her so badly,

32:30.310 --> 32:31.720
why don't you do it yourself?

32:43.480 --> 32:45.110
What do you want?

32:58.230 --> 32:59.390
Why are you here?

33:00.480 --> 33:01.570
Are you looking for me?

33:01.910 --> 33:03.430
Did you meet Bai Shuo?

33:04.260 --> 33:05.130
Yes.

33:05.260 --> 33:06.610
What did she tell you?

33:07.270 --> 33:08.550
Are you suspecting Bai Shuo?

33:08.580 --> 33:09.990
The fact that you asked this question

33:10.180 --> 33:11.660
means you're suspecting her too.

33:12.400 --> 33:14.730
I originally planned to go to the Cold Spring Palace to find the antidote.

33:14.750 --> 33:16.230
I went to say goodbye to Bai Shuo

33:16.260 --> 33:18.540
and tell her that Fu Ling is actually Bai Xi.

33:19.130 --> 33:21.770
But she told me that I could only leave Bodhi Village

33:21.790 --> 33:23.600
by killing Luan Zhu.

33:24.220 --> 33:26.170
But Bai Shuo would never ask me to kill anyone.

33:26.200 --> 33:27.650
She's not Bai Shuo.

33:28.120 --> 33:29.400
Then who is she?

33:29.590 --> 33:30.820
Where is the real Bai Shuo?

33:30.850 --> 33:32.300
There is a soul possession technique

33:32.320 --> 33:33.530
to seize one's body and exchange souls.

33:33.890 --> 33:34.880
Soul possession?

33:34.900 --> 33:36.770
The Contemplation Stone once showed a prophetic vision.

33:37.390 --> 33:39.600
Bai Shuo saw herself offering her blood to a cauldron in the vision.

33:39.790 --> 33:42.060
I did find a wound on her finger.

33:42.270 --> 33:43.380
If I'm not mistaken,

33:43.410 --> 33:44.530
her strange behavior

33:44.670 --> 33:46.230
began from there.

33:46.480 --> 33:48.180
And before she met with you,

33:48.350 --> 33:50.350
she went alone to Luan Zhu's place.

33:50.460 --> 33:51.460
Luan Zhu?

33:51.880 --> 33:53.570
You think Luan Zhu's the one who did it?

33:53.590 --> 33:55.210
In this Bodhi Village,

33:55.330 --> 33:56.570
whether it's Old Turtle,

33:56.600 --> 33:57.640
your parents,

33:57.680 --> 33:59.070
or anyone else,

33:59.100 --> 34:00.990
they all act weird.

34:01.030 --> 34:02.810
This village is under Luan Zhu's protection.

34:02.940 --> 34:04.310
It's impossible

34:04.500 --> 34:05.610
that she's not involved.

34:07.400 --> 34:08.760
Since you've come to me,

34:08.880 --> 34:10.250
you must already have a plan.

34:10.270 --> 34:11.510
To save Bai Shuo,

34:11.810 --> 34:13.389
we must first break through the fog in front of us.

34:13.420 --> 34:14.989
Since the other side has already made their move,

34:15.260 --> 34:16.920
let's turn their own tactics against them.

34:21.800 --> 34:23.170
I didn't expect

34:23.280 --> 34:25.010
I would lose because of this.

34:25.159 --> 34:26.780
You didn't lose because of this wound,

34:26.940 --> 34:28.230
but because of your mindset.

34:28.260 --> 34:30.330
The real Bai Shuo wouldn't ignore lives.

34:30.350 --> 34:32.350
She would never incite murder to achieve her goals.

34:32.469 --> 34:33.760
Where is Bai Shuo?

34:34.510 --> 34:35.510
Change her back.

34:36.820 --> 34:38.489
With the same face,

34:38.520 --> 34:39.770
I can stay by your side too,

34:39.790 --> 34:41.270
just like I did 60,000 years ago.

34:45.540 --> 34:47.090
I'll give you one last chance.

34:52.889 --> 34:55.380
The seven stars on your body have dwindled to just one,

34:55.730 --> 34:57.850
and this is your final opportunity.

34:58.120 --> 34:59.410
You want to gather all Five Contemplations.

34:59.480 --> 35:00.840
Why don't you ask me?

35:01.360 --> 35:02.690
The power of the Divine Maiden

35:02.710 --> 35:04.020
can glimpse divine Contemplations.

35:04.400 --> 35:05.390
Fan Yue,

35:05.940 --> 35:07.630
I know where the last Contemplation is.

35:08.740 --> 35:10.700
If you promise to give up on Bai Shuo

35:10.720 --> 35:12.280
and be with me from now on,

35:12.310 --> 35:14.500
I'll tell you where the final Contemplation is.

35:14.520 --> 35:15.560
What do you think?

35:16.200 --> 35:18.120
Compared to breaking the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal,

35:19.150 --> 35:20.750
I want Shuo back.

35:22.030 --> 35:23.300
To protect her,

35:23.620 --> 35:25.100
you're even willing to die?

35:25.230 --> 35:26.460
My business

35:26.840 --> 35:28.390
is none of your concern.

35:56.220 --> 35:57.670
It's so late.

35:57.850 --> 35:59.730
You don't have to bring a knife

36:00.540 --> 36:02.340
to visit me, do you?

36:17.700 --> 36:19.140
Do you think that,

36:19.170 --> 36:20.880
with the same face as theirs,

36:20.900 --> 36:22.630
you can deceive me?

36:22.650 --> 36:25.130
When it comes to those closest to you, it's not their face you recognize—

36:25.160 --> 36:26.390
it's their heart.

36:26.410 --> 36:27.850
So what if you know

36:27.880 --> 36:29.090
we're fakes?

36:29.110 --> 36:30.420
None of you

36:30.450 --> 36:32.460
will leave Bodhi Village.

36:34.690 --> 36:37.250
Have you heard of the ruthless Lady Fu Ling

36:37.280 --> 36:38.920
from the Cold Spring Palace?

36:43.180 --> 36:44.930
It hurts!

36:48.330 --> 36:50.140
You really were created using puppetry.

36:50.170 --> 36:52.110
You can't defeat the Divine Maiden.

36:53.940 --> 36:56.060
A puppet made of silk threads

36:56.550 --> 36:58.030
is not afraid of knives.

36:58.260 --> 37:00.190
But is it afraid of fire?

37:09.210 --> 37:10.270
Don't do it.

37:10.290 --> 37:11.320
What do you want to know?

37:11.350 --> 37:12.670
I...

37:12.690 --> 37:14.000
I'll tell you.

37:14.030 --> 37:16.880
Then tell me everything honestly.

37:16.900 --> 37:18.260
Who is Luan Zhu?

37:18.280 --> 37:21.030
And what secret is hidden in Bodhi Village?

37:21.800 --> 37:22.680
Alright.

37:22.700 --> 37:23.660
I'll confess.

37:23.690 --> 37:24.850
I'll confess everything.

37:55.210 --> 37:56.640
Someone is breaking the barrier?

37:57.210 --> 37:58.170
Fan Yue,

37:58.190 --> 37:59.420
you don't need to answer me right now.

37:59.450 --> 38:00.660
I'll give you time.

38:00.680 --> 38:02.000
Think about it.

38:06.390 --> 38:08.000
Shuo is trying to break through the restriction.

38:08.020 --> 38:09.930
If she forces it, she'll easily suffer backlash.

38:09.960 --> 38:10.920
Let's guard her now!

39:00.440 --> 39:02.600
This is the secret of Bodhi Village?

39:22.080 --> 39:23.390
Mystery Turtle?

39:24.520 --> 39:25.610
Mystery Turtle!

39:25.630 --> 39:26.630
Wake up!

39:27.300 --> 39:28.340
Mystery Turtle!

39:31.380 --> 39:32.630
Who are you?

39:33.780 --> 39:35.190
I'll get you out first.

39:40.280 --> 39:41.390
How do you feel?

39:42.600 --> 39:44.410
With your demon power,

39:44.960 --> 39:47.400
it's supposed to be impossible for you to break through the barrier.

40:01.320 --> 40:02.320
Shuo,

40:02.340 --> 40:03.590
why are you here?

40:03.620 --> 40:04.860
This village is dangerous.

40:04.880 --> 40:06.070
Leave now!

40:06.760 --> 40:08.580
I haven't seen you for a long time.

40:08.600 --> 40:09.960
Of course I should visit you.

40:09.990 --> 40:11.450
She's not Bai Shuo.

40:11.580 --> 40:12.670
You...

40:12.700 --> 40:14.700
Jin Yao couldn't kill you,

40:14.720 --> 40:16.380
and the barrier couldn't stop you.

40:16.530 --> 40:17.890
Fu Ling,

40:17.910 --> 40:19.270
it seems you're not simple either.

40:19.300 --> 40:19.990
You...

40:20.020 --> 40:21.500
You're Luan Zhu.

40:21.520 --> 40:23.770
You really are a 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle.

40:23.800 --> 40:26.270
Though I've absorbed most of your spiritual power,

40:26.290 --> 40:28.090
you can still see through the truth at a glance.

40:28.140 --> 40:30.170
What did you do to my disciple?

40:30.200 --> 40:31.520
Can't you tell?

40:31.630 --> 40:33.670
I'll use her body.

40:33.700 --> 40:35.550
And I'll use everything that belongs to her.

40:44.770 --> 40:45.520
You...

40:45.550 --> 40:47.120
Don't hurt her.

40:51.180 --> 40:53.190
You two are sisters.

40:53.210 --> 40:55.080
But why are you so different from each other?

40:55.110 --> 40:57.030
Should I call you Fu Ling

40:57.060 --> 40:58.830
or Bai Xi?

40:59.380 --> 41:00.860
You are Bai Xi?

41:01.570 --> 41:03.040
Kill me if you want!

41:03.060 --> 41:05.020
Of course I will kill you.

41:05.050 --> 41:07.450
But without Bai Shuo witnessing it,

41:07.640 --> 41:09.910
I feel like it'll be missing some of the fun.

41:10.370 --> 41:13.570
What did you do to my disciple?

41:32.240 --> 41:34.520
Shuo! Shuo!

41:36.460 --> 41:37.470
Bai Shuo,

41:37.760 --> 41:39.280
this is such a great show;

41:39.770 --> 41:41.290
you really should watch it.

41:41.320 --> 41:42.340
Luan Zhu,

41:42.370 --> 41:44.390
if you dare harm my master and Fu Ling,

41:44.420 --> 41:45.940
I will not let you go!

41:46.780 --> 41:49.410
You can't even protect yourself.

41:49.430 --> 41:51.040
What do you think you can do to me?

41:51.060 --> 41:51.940
Luan Zhu,

41:51.970 --> 41:54.050
just absorb my spiritual power.

41:54.070 --> 41:56.170
Let my disciple go.

41:59.520 --> 42:01.560
I do plan to absorb your spiritual power.

42:01.590 --> 42:02.990
Jin Yao has been hesitating

42:03.010 --> 42:05.570
and hasn't brought in new Eternals yet.

42:06.010 --> 42:07.620
Your 1000 year of spiritual power

42:07.640 --> 42:09.690
is the best supplement right now.

42:14.700 --> 42:15.980
Master!

42:17.930 --> 42:19.140
Stop!

42:24.390 --> 42:26.760
Bai Shuo,

42:26.780 --> 42:29.040
I want you to watch

42:29.060 --> 42:32.310
as your closest ones die one by one right in front of you.

42:41.010 --> 42:45.970
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

42:49.130 --> 42:54.760
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

42:57.420 --> 43:04.850
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

43:05.110 --> 43:06.490
Stop it!

43:05.770 --> 43:10.820
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

43:06.730 --> 43:08.290
Stop it!

43:12.930 --> 43:14.260
Master!

43:30.830 --> 43:32.450
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

43:32.710 --> 43:34.680
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

43:35.000 --> 43:36.430
♫My love brought tears♫

43:36.870 --> 43:38.590
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

43:39.180 --> 43:40.750
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

43:41.090 --> 43:42.250
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

43:42.660 --> 43:44.100
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

43:44.630 --> 43:46.110
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

43:46.870 --> 43:48.210
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

43:48.590 --> 43:50.120
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

43:50.780 --> 43:52.470
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

43:52.920 --> 43:54.640
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

43:55.080 --> 43:56.750
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

43:57.090 --> 43:58.870
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

43:59.290 --> 44:00.720
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

44:01.160 --> 44:03.400
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

44:03.660 --> 44:04.800
-Shuo!
-Shuo!

44:05.840 --> 44:07.040
You're back.

44:07.070 --> 44:08.070
Let's go to the cave now.

44:08.090 --> 44:09.370
My master is in danger!
